Command,Description
"find . -type f -name ""f1.txt""",Find a specific file in the current directory
"find . -type d -name ""dir""",Find a directory by name
find . -type f -empty,Find all empty files
find . -perm 777,Find files with 777 permissions
find / -user <name>,Find files owned by a specific user
find . -mmin -60,Files modified in the last hour
find . -size +50M,Files larger than 50MB
"grep ""word"" file",Search for a string inside a file
"grep -i ""word"" file",Case-insensitive search
"grep -r ""word"" .",Recursive search for string in all files
